{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't have anything to give up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were being searched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we were told to go in to a place, and-- for [? entlousen, ?] you know, to-- to be cleansed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we did as we were told.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we figured that's going to be the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Apparently, when we arrived in Auschwitz, we arrived there with a permit or with some instructions, because we were experienced ammunition workers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "There was no selection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Those who were alive, dis-- alive, disembarked from the wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We were marched towards the-- the crematoria nearby, which was the [? entlousing ?] chambers, where we took the showers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There was no selection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Therefore, I would have never made it to Auschwitz, because I was too small.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Because there was no selection, I made it through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we were given a shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We were [? entloused. ?] Then we went out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We were given some-- like this striped clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Of course, it didn't fit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Of course, this-- this wasn't-- didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We were again assembled and marched away, which was around the corner, through some camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we were assigned to go into the gypsy camp, the Zigeunerlager.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
